article_title: Route 259 Lift Bridge closed for weekend
article_text:
March 12, 2016 06:28 PM

The Department of Transportation reports that the Route 259 Lift Bridge in the Village of Spencerport is closed to traffic this weekend.

The lift bridge was closed to traffic at 7 a.m. Saturday morning, and is expected to remain closed through Sunday evening until it is completed.
